Tutorial¶

This is a simple tutorial meant to show GsshaPy users how to use the GsshaPy ORM objects.

Sample Data¶

A set of example GSSHA model files can be downloaded here. Unzip the contents of the file. This file will become the working directory for the tutorial. The tutorial-data/write directory is purposely left empty.
